{"tid":19517,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（穆斯林系列2）耶女拒絕轉信伊斯蘭，被綁架強姦","createTime":"2016-12-02T23:23:27.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-03T01:03:53.000Z","uid":29314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c810c933b1ffc1dd87ba6d7f4611cb34f0077846","tid":19517,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T23:23:27.000Z","msg":"位於倫敦的慈善機構英國巴基斯坦基督徒協會(The British Pakistani Christian Association，簡稱BPCA)說，這家人&hellip;&hellip;不斷被當地穆斯林施加壓力，改信伊斯蘭教，他們是社區中唯一沒有接受伊斯蘭教的家庭。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n9月15日晚上，一隊6名穆斯林男女拿着槍、木棍、鐵棒&hellip;&hellip;狠狠地毆打了這家基督徒。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;一家人仍然拒絕否認基督和改信伊斯蘭教。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n這家人拒絕改信之後，穆斯林變得憤怒起來，&hellip;&hellip;拉走了這家17歲的女兒賈米勒(Jameela)和20歲的兒子阿里夫(Arif)，&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;一個抓他們過來的人告訴阿里夫，其他穆斯林男人在輪姦他的妹妹，他能夠救她的唯一辦法就是接受伊斯蘭教。"},{"pid":"605e53b23ca77f90e3ddd0f603ee77cc4e4aae25","tid":19517,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T23:25:34.000Z","msg":"被襲擊和綁架后，這個基督徒家庭先去找穆斯林僱主，他不但告訴他們去對警察說，而且命令他們第二天回去幹活。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">這家人試圖指控警察，然而卡蘇爾當地警察拒絕註冊這一案件。&nbsp;</span><br />\n<br />\n警察局甚至被巴基斯坦議員施加壓力，註冊警方報告。<br />\n<br />\n然而，副警官拒絕註冊這一案件。"},{"pid":"fef3a512f233a73f38abb5ecdd76ecb5b7a1b00c","tid":19517,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T23:36:33.000Z","msg":"英國都咁on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b913cd52632a64d21feb185b7c9d8c1410e1e35","tid":19517,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T23:57:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>英國都咁on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係islam on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"156badc387076c8d3292a6bedad99d7368767a2d","tid":19517,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T00:20:32.000Z","msg":"大愛左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n燒山講兩句然後好返過紅登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73328ab3dcbff47d8a2e3f41deda2d284189f3b0","tid":19517,"uid":28023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T00:28:46.000Z","msg":"發生喺巴基斯坦。。。。<br />\n<br />\n不過d source 只係來自基督教網站，唔知思覺脫巴想quote 嚟做乜"},{"pid":"92f434e9329233a9ca84564c6bc386d7f7bff5ac","tid":19517,"uid":12362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T00:49:52.000Z","msg":"轉信左只不過由強姦變做做雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08167d4a8eeacc763ae588062a39f5a710ada174","tid":19517,"uid":50088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T00:55:04.000Z","msg":"姐係我都想信<br />\n但乜source都冇。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"271b0a107158303e6296c79a9a9971c9eb55cba3","tid":19517,"uid":23902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T01:03:53.000Z","msg":"無source難講喎<br />\n利申好憎伊斯籣"}]}